# Security audit

- Audit this extension with OWASP/PHP priorities: injection, XSS, CSRF, unsafe trust boundaries, secrets exposure, and insecure parsing.
- Re-check issues already noted by TYPO3-specific security review, but keep only findings not already resolved.
- Prefer code-level remediations with clear risk reduction and minimal behavior change.
- Call out cases that are documentation or integrator responsibilities instead of extension code defects.

## Report loop

- Write findings to `Build/Reports/security-audit-report.md`.
- Commit the report before remediation.
- If no new actionable issues remain after review, skip the changes commit.
